Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}vol.1\NFind Momoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have the same initials as Marilyn Monroe: M.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Morita Momoko, age 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm an actress in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been to countless auditions so far,\Nbut I haven't gotten a break yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Momoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm working at my part-time job right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jeez, look at all the people around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At least one of them could bother to look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cities really are unfriendly places.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A potentially catchable salaryman!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I wonder why he's been\Nwaiting there for over an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she stand you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, this mannequin looks almost human!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't move, can she?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, what a realistic mannequin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, she's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she's squishy. I'd like to do her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop these jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy, guys. We're in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the fuck put you in charge, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. They took him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't be so rough with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man! You have a lot of nerve,\Nlatching onto us like a clam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! What school do you punks go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By intruding on the scene, you've totally\Nmessed up the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an undercover cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I send you guys off to\Njuvie to make some friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-kun! You shouldn't leave your post!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Now you've made my boss mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit! Let's run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't desert your post. I'm paying\Nyou money to work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think I should explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, on second thought, you can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a woman with a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you don't mean I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}do{\i0} mean it. You're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you're waiting for,\Nbut nobody should make you wait three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet it's a girl you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be really sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm a bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un, well, it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A bit"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. Why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I wanted to go to a formal dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll stop off at home and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was really looking forward to this party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're late too, you hypocrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a rotten personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go alone tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you at work tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make excuses for you there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mean bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, listen, you should just\Ndump that stupid woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thanked you for\Nhelping me out back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made you lose your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, will you be my new job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll live with you and provide everything in\Nyour life that doesn't relate to your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, my rent, employment, and\Nsexual needs will all be taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you just described is marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it doesn't need to be so formal,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as we both agree to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any complaints\Nabout my body, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to live with Momoko,\Nthe Japanese Marilyn Monroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was being serious, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please spare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kentaro, don't tell me you're\Nengaged to that bitchy woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my boss's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave her, and you'll move on in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you actually like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only with her to advance my career.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't... anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not being yourself, Kentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hongoh, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You live in a pretty nice place, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can touch me whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never wear a bra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, I'll claim this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't fall asleep on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm carrying you, so you'd better make\Nlove to me when we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Minami Kentaro, Ochiai Haruo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, it's hard to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you sleep in your own bed, Haruo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haruo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai! Who the hell is that in your bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who? Isn't it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are there two of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Stop sleepwalking and talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, I didn't know you\Nwere that kind of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After spending years at prestigious\NTokvo U, I couldn't have imagined this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Marilyn Monroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monroe? And you say {\i1}I'm{\i0} sleepwalking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you cuddling with her just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I wonder if we did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Capital Hongoh
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be safe, I think I should\Naccompany you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she's a business\Nwoman, she's still a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... I probably shouldn't have got drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the least of your problems, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's this late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who is this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, I-I'm Ochiai Haruo, a classmate of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm his roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kentaro, I thought you lived alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Uh, um, well... I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Morita Momoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make us some breakfast, so sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. What do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, Momoko-san... a-a skirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? If it bothers you, I'll put one on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it doesn't bother me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Momoko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did I promise that you could live with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Kentaro, shouldn't you be leaving for work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's have a nice day today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right, Kentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave your laundry out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash it later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sales Business Department
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just finished tidying up, and\NI'm about to take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where's Haruo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him? He fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kentaro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. He hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna peep, then just go\Nahead and peep shamelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, it's bad for your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go collect my belongings,\Nso you take care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you mad at me for going\Nto the party alone last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you to dinner tonight, as an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, it's my turn to cook tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good timing then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask my father's restaurant\Nto send food to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, but this is so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind. You don't need\Nto hold back on my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll meet you at 7:00 at your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}7 00...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Momoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oteru? I've got big news for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oteru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the big mess you've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess this should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oteru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are we in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't know you'd be back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found someplace else to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man even handsomer than George Marley.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Kentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about being an actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was just a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Momoko-san is coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She only left to fetch her belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then... she's coming back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, don't let her back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she left her bag behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something slithered out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... It's an iguana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Haruo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But it's coming this way, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, dear? Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my pet, Wilder, from the\NGalapagos Islands. Hope ya like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's housebroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was drunk. I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And engaged or not, you'd better take\Nresponsibility for your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruo, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've made her cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually, the girl you met\Nin Ginza is coming at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you're here too, it will be awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand the position I'm in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Momoko-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything to make this up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Reiko-san? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, doesn't she want me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Didn't she want me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says a friend from Paris is\Nvisiting, so she can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many floors in this building?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Building!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, that's not what a meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just please cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life is so pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a girl cry? What a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I'll go to some more auditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where should she sleep then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's in here, she'll disrupt your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko-san is going to sleep\Nin bed with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess sh-she thinks so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think I'll go sleep\Ndownstairs under a sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just do what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a bed for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you just sleep with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me clarify a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're living together,\Nlet's keep some privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to sleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no fun, Kentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One boring sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two boring sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three boring sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four boring sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five boring sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six boring sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven boring sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight boring sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep with that racket!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's do something fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't with you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't sleep unless I'm naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Coco Chanel, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko looks like Marilyn Monroe, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it, Kentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wilder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like the Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be our lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galapagos...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shouldn't I be able to watch at least\Na little, for future reference?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came. I came. I came. I came...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what if I get pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I keep it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.63,0:22:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm on the pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.97,0:22:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really surreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to be strangers,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we met under the city lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and made love there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're finally interested in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.33,0:23:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Onomichi in Hiroshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's surrounded by mountains and the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born on a farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. We grew fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a middle child.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My big sister is Nashiko and\Nmy little sister is Kuriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Note: "Nashiko" means pear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Note: "Kuriko" means chesnut.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Note: "Momoko" means peach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm... Momoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family is full of fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a strange family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of people say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That we're strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bathed with my father until I\Nstarted going to high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.91,0:23:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd always scrub my chest and butt.\NThat's why I'm so well developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Momoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.62,0:23:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a woman too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're soft and supple on the outside,\Nbut juicy on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes a perfect woman\Nand a perfect peach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a perverted thing for your father to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a pedophile!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.89,0:24:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me there is only one\Npeach in the entire world,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that I should become that peach.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.73,0:24:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Marilyn Monroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.74,0:24:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you want to be an actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.03,0:24:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.24,0:24:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if this is all a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.12,0:24:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm also {\i1}your{\i0} Momoko, Kentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.79,0:24:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.62,0:24:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's go for another round.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.59,0:24:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last time ended too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.95,0:25:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruo,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.16,0:25:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your eyes are pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.70,0:25:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.70,0:25:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.66,0:25:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like someone's tied you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.50,0:25:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wilder, must you always be so greedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.26,0:25:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.26,0:25:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you stop eating that, it'll all be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.18,0:25:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you feed him anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.18,0:25:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cactus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.64,0:25:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cactus?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.02,0:25:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.77,0:25:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can always buy you another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.81,0:25:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I'm gonna find\Na job and get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.12,0:25:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm gonna try an adult video audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.54,0:25:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adult videos?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.29,0:25:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure, Momoko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.04,0:25:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.83,0:25:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already practiced for it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.84,0:25:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.18,0:25:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.14,0:26:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.23,0:26:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you set for the next 24 hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.31,0:26:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's natural for my lifestyle\Nto change drastically overnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.44,0:26:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then learn so much about women so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.74,0:26:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Momoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.37,0:26:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.04,0:26:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.88,0:26:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chief, you're a woman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.18,0:26:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.35,0:26:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...though an aged fruit is a different matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.68,0:26:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's only me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.68,0:26:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only person who thinks you're not smart\Nenough to have graduated from Tokyo U.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.60,0:26:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami-kun, you're the chosen one!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.15,0:26:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.57,0:26:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you fell into that woman's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.24,0:26:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.07,0:26:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.57,0:27:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you weren't engaged\Nto your boss's daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.32,0:27:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd still have a bright future ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.12,0:27:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to my exalted position\Nby cutting men's throats.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.71,0:27:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Position...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.33,0:27:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I would love to have graduated from\NTokyo U and be married at age 32,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.84,0:27:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess that an affair is\Nall I've got left right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.55,0:27:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chief, you have a meeting today, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.93,0:27:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the head of Personnel, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.89,0:27:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kawakami Reiko, your fiancée,\Nsays she wants to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.44,0:27:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.86,0:27:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.44,0:27:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, may I borrow Minami-san for a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.90,0:27:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.11,0:27:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.29,0:27:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Reiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.41,0:27:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.41,0:27:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend from Paris came back all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.04,0:27:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and brought me a beautiful present.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.38,0:27:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to show it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.67,0:28:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.13,0:28:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chanel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.59,0:28:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chanel?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.07,0:28:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.28,0:28:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Isn't it stylish?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.63,0:28:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.14,0:28:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, um, weren't you going to a video audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.31,0:28:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was lying, hoping Kentaro would stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.02,0:28:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.23,0:28:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you know of any good jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.61,0:29:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's unskilled labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.40,0:29:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That would fit me perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.99,0:29:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.41,0:29:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, it's a job where you need to wear a bra.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.45,0:29:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boob-band, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.08,0:29:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't own one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.87,0:29:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go buy you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.34,0:29:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.55,0:29:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.51,0:29:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you won't regret this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.10,0:29:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.94,0:29:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Personnel Department | User Interview Conference Room
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.77,0:29:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.73,0:29:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.40,0:29:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.24,0:29:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.74,0:29:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.20,0:29:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young people these days have no manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.17,0:29:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.09,0:30:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.63,0:30:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's start with your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.01,0:30:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Morita Momoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.55,0:30:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.43,0:30:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.94,0:30:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you wish to join our company?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.61,0:30:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.96,0:30:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In today's society, there's a question of what\Nrole electronics will play in women's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.42,0:30:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe this is an important issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.47,0:30:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I believe that in order to make the most\Nefficient use of their time and money,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.47,0:30:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,women must become\Ncomfortable with electronics.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.77,0:31:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I want to research ways to\Nincrease efficiency in the workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.95,0:31:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Morita-san, do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.04,0:31:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.75,0:31:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a humble salaryman, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.54,0:31:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he graduate from college?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.29,0:31:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo U.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.79,0:31:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you.
