Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.05,0:31:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to take care of\Nhim and understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.31,0:31:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's got balls.
