Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.70,0:32:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.45,0:32:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might faint again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.21,0:32:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.08,0:32:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.71,0:32:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
