Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.55,0:32:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.38,0:32:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That feels much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.26,0:32:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko, you'd better withdraw\Nyour application and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.18,0:33:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... did they hire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.52,0:33:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief liked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.61,0:33:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.07,0:33:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.95,0:33:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've passed an audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.74,0:33:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Momoko! If someone\Nsees you here like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.87,0:33:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.50,0:33:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.76,0:33:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.18,0:33:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a little celebration for you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.64,0:33:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy that you're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.10,0:33:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, Kentaro, the boss is calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.06,0:33:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.89,0:33:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't you skip out on the new\Ngirl's party and take Reiko out instead?
